1. Typo in translation key: sortAutomatially
   File: src/components/HamburgerMenu/Menu.jsx:27
   Type: potential_issue
   Status: Pre-existing

   The key 'settings.sortAutomatially' is missing the letter 'c' (should be
   'sortAutomatically'). Both the source code and translations.json use the
   misspelled key consistently, so it works correctly. Fixing requires updating
   the key in both Menu.jsx and translations.json simultaneously.

2. Clickable divs lack keyboard accessibility
   File: src/components/HamburgerMenu/Menu.jsx:22-37
   Type: potential_issue (accessibility)
   Status: Pre-existing

   Menu items use onClick on <div> elements without keyboard support (role,
   tabIndex, onKeyDown). Should use <button> elements or add role="button",
   tabIndex={0}, and onKeyDown handlers for Enter/Space.

3. React Router v7 future flags warnings
   File: docs/react-migration-tasks/03-implementation-log.md:71-74
   Type: potential_issue
   Status: Pre-existing (from Phase 3)

   Warnings about v7_startTransition and v7_relativeSplatPath indicate the
   router config doesn't enable future flags for v7 compatibility. Should add
   future={{ v7_startTransition: true, v7_relativeSplatPath: true }} to
   BrowserRouter props when ready.
